起点金额由 500 元上调至 600 元，后续将持续关注黄金市场变动情况，适时对上述起点金额及限额进行调整。 复旦大学金融研究院兼职研究员 董希淼：在黄金市场价格上涨较快的情况下，相关银行对起点金额进行调整，以更好适应黄金市场变化。黄金价格时有波动，投资黄金并非稳赚不赔。投资者要基于自身投资理财的目标和需求，适当配置黄金产品，切勿跟风投资、追涨杀跌。金价「狂飙」！国有大行发布公告：上调金额！金价还会继续涨吗？专家解读 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b2eac86475715552c6dc1bcdae20c77f_b.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "74 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/647914194"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IhIi6z8XuvJJCEAMaCTEwNjI1ODEzNiDT/7WvBjAAOC1ADnIJNjQ3OTE0MTk0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1710141406.977437", "card_id": "Q_646561627", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 232}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么家长辅导孩子作业，容易发疯？问题出在哪里？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-f85ca374ed0e204fef433662f18189ec_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "72 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/646561627"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIhIi6z8XuvJJCEAMaCTEwNTk1ODAyMiDc4YSvBjAAOI8CQA9yCTY0NjU2MTYyN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1710141406.978074", "card_id": "Q_647077814", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 38}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "「热烈的爱情」和「稳定的情绪」可以并存吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "今日和朋友讨论，越热烈的爱，就会激发占有欲，就会越计较，就会情绪失控！可是大家都喜欢稳定情绪的人，那是不是情绪稳定那个人就不太爱对方呢，无欲则刚是不是就说明问题了。 好矛盾，好像这个论题是对的，又觉得哪里不对，所以问问大家的看法"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-0d5ef96afb2a39282d47e68cb1e438a3_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "l